ORIGIN NOTE

Portions of this repository originate as an extraction from the `/mkg/`
directory of a proprietary clinical decision support system authored by
the same copyright holder. The extracted code has been re-licensed under
Apache-2.0 by the same copyright holder, and restructured to:

  - Consume `crkg-schema` (Apache-2.0) as the data contract source
  - Abstract graph backend access behind a `GraphStore` Protocol
  - Replace direct traditional-medicine ingestion with a pluggable
    `TraditionalMedicineAdapter` Protocol
  - Remove any hardcoded coupling to proprietary data sources

The original `/mkg/` directory is retired from its origin project in the
same release cycle that this package publishes its first stable version
(v0.1.0). No long-term duplicate code is maintained.

See `docs/MIGRATION_FROM_MKG.md` for details.

