CLINICAL TERMINOLOGY REFERENCES

This package parses formats from several clinical and biomedical
terminology systems but does NOT redistribute, embed, or bundle them.
Deployers populating `crkg` with data from these systems remain
responsible for compliance with each system's license and terms of use:

  - ICD-11 (WHO)                    — https://icd.who.int/
  - ICD-10-CM (CMS)                 — https://www.cms.gov/
  - SNOMED CT (SNOMED International) — https://www.snomed.org/
  - LOINC (Regenstrief)             — https://loinc.org/
  - RxNorm (NLM)                    — https://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm/
  - ATC (WHO CC)                    — https://www.whocc.no/atc/
  - MeSH (NLM)                      — https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/mesh/

Some require registration, affiliate licensing, or UMLS authentication
to access. `crkg` does not and cannot distribute content from them.
